{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312031218ccc29760b63c481d","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"id":"20260312031218ccc29760b63c481d","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_24a94e3328b44d41b0431143","name":"Task","input":{"description":"PM: Specify, Plan, Tasks for F-003","prompt":"Read /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.codebuddy/agents/prizm-dev-team-pm.md. For feature F-003 (slug: 003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion), complete all three planning steps in this single session:\n\n1. Run prizmkit-specify → generate `.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/spec.md`. If there are `[NEEDS CLARIFICATION]` markers, run prizmkit-clarify to resolve them.\n\n2. Run prizmkit-plan → generate `.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/plan.md` (architecture, components, interface design, data model, testing strategy, risk assessment — all in one file)\n\n3. Run prizmkit-tasks → generate `.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/tasks.md` with `[ ]` checkboxes\n\nAll three files go under `.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/`.\n\nFeature Description: 实现 Telegram 侧计划文件接入能力，支持 feature-list.json 与 bug-fix-list.json 的上传、引用与落盘管理。系统需完成 JSON 解析、schema 校验、错误定位、版本化存储与回滚选择，使用户能在 Telegram 中完成\"提供计划输入\"的闭环。该功能需兼容 app-planner/bug-planner 产物格式，并为后续 pipeline 执行提供稳定输入路径。\n\nAcceptance Criteria:\n- 支持通过 Telegram 上传或引用计划文件并成功保存到约定目录\n- 对 feature-list 与 bug-fix-list 执行 schema 校验，失败时返回字段级错误\n- 支持同名文件版本化管理，并可指定某个版本作为当前执行输入\n- 当输入文件不合法时，不会污染当前可运行配置且会保留原有稳定版本\n- 保存成功后可被 pipeline 控制层直接读取并启动执行\n\nDependencies (Already Completed):\n- F-001 - Project Infrastructure Setup\n- F-002 - Telegram Pipeline Command Router\n\nApp Global Context:\n- design_system: Telegram command UX with structured message templates\n- language: TypeScript\n- tech_stack: Node.js + Express + Telegraf + JSON state files + Shell/Python dev-pipeline\n- testing_strategy: Jest (unit + integration)","run_in_background":false,"subagent_type":"prizm-dev-team-pm","