{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312031304b857bd8488f3488d","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"id":"20260312031304b857bd8488f3488d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I'll generate the three planning documents. Starting with `spec.md`:"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_24a94e3328b44d41b0431143","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:13:27.165Z","_requestId":"553c6d77d2214d40857e104dd24ea2b3"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312031304b857bd8488f3488d","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"id":"20260312031304b857bd8488f3488d","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde512c243b349d80d701f8c6351d","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/spec.md","content":"# F-003: Feature and Bug Plan Ingestion\n\n## Summary\n\n实现 Telegram 侧计划文件接入能力，支持 feature-list.json 与 bug-fix-list.json 的上传、引用与落盘管理。系统需完成 JSON 解析、schema 校验、错误定位、版本化存储与回滚选择，使用户能在 Telegram 中完成\"提供计划输入\"的闭环。\n\n**Scope**: 文件上传处理、JSON schema 校验、版本化存储、版本切换与回滚、与 pipeline 控制层集成。\n\n**Dependencies**: F-001 (Project Infrastructure Setup) — completed, F-002 (Telegram Pipeline Command Router) — completed\n\n---\n\n## User Stories\n\n### US-1: Upload Plan File\n\n作为授权用户，我可以通过 Telegram 上传 feature-list.json 或 bug-fix-list.json 文件，系统自动识别类型并保存。\n\n**Example**:\n- 用户在 Telegram 中发送 JSON 文件\n- 系统识别文件类型（通过 `$schema` 字段）\n- 系统执行 schema 校验\n- 校验通过后保存到版本目录\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 支持 Telegram document 消息接收\n- 自动识别 feature-list 和 bug-fix-list 类型\n- 返回接收确认与文件摘要\n\n---\n\n### US-2: Schema Validation\n\n作为授权用户，当我上传的计划文件不符合 schema 时，系统返回字段级错误信息帮助我修正。\n\n**Example**:\n- 用户上传缺少必填字段的 JSON\n- 系统返回错误：`features[0].id: 缺少必填字段`\n- 用户根据提示修正后重新上传\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 使用现有 dev-pipeline/templates/*.json 进行校验\n- 错误信息包含字段路径、错误类型、建议修正\n- 不合法文件不会被保存为生效版本\n\n---\n\n### US-3: Version Management\n\n作为授权用户，我可以查看同一计划文件的历史版本，并指定某个版本作为当前执行输入。\n\n**Example**:\n- `/plan versions feature-list` — 列出所有版本\n- `/plan use feature-list v2` — 切换到 v2 版本\n- `/plan rollback feature-list` — 回滚到上一版本\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 每次上传生成新版本（时间戳命名）\n- 支持版本列表查看\n- 支持版本切换与回滚\n- 当前生效版本有明确标识\n\n---\n\n### US-4: Plan Status Query\n\n作为授权用户，我可以查看当前生效的计划文件状态。\n\n**Example**:\n- `/plan status` — 显示当前 feature-list 和 bug-fix-list 状态\n- 显示：文件路径、版本号、特性/bug 数量、最后更新时间\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 显示当前生效版本信息\n- 显示文件内容摘要（特性/bug 数量、状态分布）\n\n---\n\n### US-5: Plan Integrity Protection\n\n作为系统，我需要确保不合法的计划文件不会污染当前可运行配置。\n\n**Example**:\n- 用户上传格式错误的 JSON\n- 校验失败，原文件保持不变\n- 错误版本被隔离存储供排查\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 校验失败的文件不覆盖当前生效版本\n- 错误文件保存到隔离目录（可选）\n- 保留原有稳定版本可继续执行\n\n---\n\n### US-6: Pipeline Integration\n\n作为系统，保存成功的计划文件需要能被 pipeline 控制层直接读取并启动执行。\n\n**Example**:\n- 用户上传新的 feature-list.json 并激活\n- 用户执行 `/pipeline run`\n- Pipeline 使用新上传的计划文件\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 与 pipeline-control-service 集成\n- 支持动态切换计划文件路径\n- 启动 pipeline 时可指定计划文件版本\n\n---\n\n## Non-Functional Requirements\n\n### NFR-1: Reliability\n\n- 文件操作原子性：写入失败不破坏现有文件\n- 版本切换幂等性：多次切换到同一版本结果一致\n\n### NFR-2: Performance\n\n- 文件上传处理 < 2s（不含网络传输）\n- Schema 校验 < 500ms（对于 100KB 文件）\n- 版本列表查询 < 100ms\n\n### NFR-3: Usability\n\n- 错误信息可读、可操作\n- 版本命名直观（时间戳或序号）\n- Telegram 消息格式友好\n\n---\n\n## Scope Boundaries\n\n### In Scope\n\n- Telegram 文件上传接收\n- JSON schema 校验（复用现有 schema 文件）\n- 版本化存储管理\n- 版本切换与回滚命令\n- 与 pipeline-control-service 集成\n- 错误信息格式化与返回\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- app-planner/bug-planner 技能实现（已有）\n- Pipeline 执行逻辑（已有）\n- Web UI 计划文件管理\n- 远程文件 URL 下载\n- 文件内容编辑\n\n---\n\n## Command Reference\n\n| Command | Subcommands | Params | Description |\n|---------|-------------|--------|-------------|\n| `/plan` | upload | — | 上传计划文件（通过文件消息） |\n| `/plan` | status | `[type]` | 查看计划状态 |\n| `/plan` | versions | `<type>` | 列出历史版本 |\n| `/plan` | use | `<type> <version>` | 切换到指定版本 |\n| `/plan` | rollback | `<type>` | 回滚到上一版本 |\n| `/plan` | validate | — | 校验当前文件（通过文件消息） |\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n\n| ID | Date | Decision |\n|----|------|----------|\n| D1 | 2026-03-12 | 版本目录结构：`plans/{type}/v{timestamp}.json` |\n| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 当前生效版本通过 symlink 或 meta.json 标识 |\n| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 复用 F-002 的命令路由基础设施 |\n| D4 | 2026-03-12 | Schema 校验使用 Ajv 或 zod（与项目技术栈一致） |\n"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":53410,"output_tokens":1372,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_24a94e3328b44d41b0431143","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:13:27.173Z","_requestId":"553c6d77d2214d40857e104dd24ea2b3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"c140aaa2-7892-4db5-9b57-3d1aac47a49b","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde512c243b349d80d701f8c6351d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully created and wrote to new file: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/spec.md"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_24a94e3328b44d41b0431143","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:13:27.191Z","_requestId":"553c6d77d2214d40857e104dd24ea2b3"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031203132710f33749c4054494","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"id":"2026031203132710f33749c4054494","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now creating `plan.md`:</think>"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_24a94e3328b44d41b0431143","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:14:25.081Z","_requestId":"553c6d77d2214d40857e104dd24ea2b3"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031203132710f33749c4054494","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"id":"2026031203132710f33749c4054494","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde51831e7da229e5cfdb076af832","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion/plan.md","content":"# F-003: Technical Implementation Plan\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Telegram Bot Entry                       │\n│                   src/bot/telegram.js                        │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n│  │ Document Handler (new)                                   ││\n│  │ - Listen for document messages                           ││\n│  │ - Filter JSON files                                      ││\n│  │ - Delegate to plan-ingestion-service                     ││\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   Command Router (F-002)                     │\n│              src/bot/commands/index.js                       │\n│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │\n│  │ /plan        │  │ /plan status │  │ /plan use    │      │\n│  │ handler      │  │ handler      │  │ handler      │      │\n│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                Plan Ingestion Service                        │\n│          src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js              │\n│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │\n│  │ Schema       │  │ Version      │  │ Plan         │      │\n│  │ Validator    │  │ Manager      │  │ Registry     │      │\n│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Pipeline Control Service (F-001)                │\n│          src/services/pipeline-control-service.js            │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n│  │ - Accepts listPath parameter for dynamic plan switching  ││\n│  │ - Integrates with plan registry for version resolution   ││\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    File Storage Layer                        │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n│  │ plans/                                                    ││\n│  │ ├── feature-list/                                        ││\n│  │ │   ├── v20260312-143052.json                           ││\n│  │ │   ├── v20260312-160321.json                           ││\n│  │ │   └── _current.json -> v20260312-160321.json          ││\n│  │ └── bug-fix-list/                                        ││\n│  │     ├── v20260312-143100.json                           ││\n│  │     └── _current.json                                    ││\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Component Design\n\n### 1. Plan Validator (`src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`)\n\n**Purpose**: 验证计划文件是否符合 schema 规范。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\ninterface ValidationResult {\n  valid: boolean;\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list' | 'unknown';\n  errors: ValidationError[];\n  summary?: PlanSummary;\n}\n\ninterface ValidationError {\n  path: string;        // JSON path, e.g., \"features[0].id\"\n  message: string;     // Human-readable error\n  keyword?: string;    // JSON Schema keyword\n}\n\ninterface PlanSummary {\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list';\n  name: string;        // app_name or project_name\n  itemCount: number;   // features or bugs count\n  statusBreakdown: Record<string, number>;\n}\n\nfunction validatePlanFile(content: string): ValidationResult;\n```\n\n**Logic**:\n1. 解析 JSON 内容\n2. 识别 `$schema` 字段确定类型\n3. 加载对应 schema 文件（从 dev-pipeline/templates/）\n4. 执行 Ajv 校验\n5. 转换错误信息为用户友好格式\n6. 生成内容摘要\n\n---\n\n### 2. Version Manager (`src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`)\n\n**Purpose**: 管理计划文件的版本化存储。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\ninterface VersionInfo {\n  version: string;      // e.g., \"v20260312-143052\"\n  timestamp: Date;\n  size: number;         // bytes\n  itemCount: number;\n  isValid: boolean;\n}\n\ninterface SaveResult {\n  success: boolean;\n  version?: string;\n  error?: string;\n}\n\nfunction savePlanVersion(\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list',\n  content: string,\n  meta: { validatedBy: string }\n): Promise<SaveResult>;\n\nfunction listVersions(\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'\n): Promise<VersionInfo[]>;\n\nfunction getVersionContent(\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list',\n  version: string\n): Promise<string | null>;\n\nfunction setCurrentVersion(\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list',\n  version: string\n): Promise<boolean>;\n\nfunction getCurrentVersion(\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'\n): Promise<string | null>;\n\nfunction rollbackVersion(\n  type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'\n): Promise<{ previousVersion: string; currentVersion: string } | null>;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Plan Registry (`src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js`)\n\n**Purpose**: 维护当前生效版本与元数据。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\ninterface PlanRegistry {\n  getActivePath(type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'): string;\n  getActiveMeta(type: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list'): ActiveMeta | null;\n  refresh(): void;\n}\n\ninterface ActiveMeta {\n  version: string;\n  path: string;\n  lastModified: Date;\n  itemCount: number;\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation**:\n- 使用 `_current.json` 文件存储当前版本信息\n- 或使用 symlink 指向当前版本文件\n- 提供 `getActivePath()` 供 pipeline-control-service 使用\n\n---\n\n### 4. Command Handlers\n\n#### Plan Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js`)\n\n```typescript\ninterface PlanParams {\n  action: 'status' | 'versions' | 'use' | 'rollback' | 'validate';\n  type?: 'feature-list' | 'bug-fix-list';\n  version?: string;\n}\n\nasync function handlePlan(ctx: Context, params: PlanParams): Promise<void>;\n```\n\n**Mapping to plan-ingestion-service**:\n- `status` → `getCurrentVersion()` + `getActiveMeta()`\n- `versions` → `listVersions()`\n- `use` → `setCurrentVersion()`\n- `rollback` → `rollbackVersion()`\n- `validate` → 手动触发校验（通过文件消息）\n\n---\n\n### 5. Document Handler (`src/bot/telegram.js` extension)\n\n**Purpose**: 处理 Telegram 文档消息，识别并保存计划文件。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\nasync function handleDocumentUpload(ctx: Context): Promise<void>;\n\n// Logic:\n// 1. Check file extension (.json)\n// 2. Download file content\n// 3. Call validatePlanFile()\n// 4. If valid, call savePlanVersion()\n// 5. Return result with formatted message\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Models\n\n### PlanStorageConfig\n```typescript\ninterface PlanStorageConfig {\n  plansDir: string;           // e.g., \"/project/plans\"\n  featureListDir: string;     // plansDir/feature-list\n  bugFixListDir: string;      // plansDir/bug-fix-list\n  maxVersions: number;        // Optional: limit version count\n  schemaPaths: {\n    featureList: string;      // dev-pipeline/templates/feature-list-schema.json\n    bugFixList: string;       // dev-pipeline/templates/bug-fix-list-schema.json\n  };\n}\n```\n\n### VersionFile\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": \"v20260312-143052\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-12T14:30:52Z\",\n  \"uploadedBy\": 12345678,\n  \"itemCount\": 5,\n  \"checksum\": \"sha256:abc123...\"\n}\n```\n\n### CurrentMeta\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": \"v20260312-143052\",\n  \"activatedAt\": \"2026-03-12T14:31:00Z\",\n  \"activatedBy\": 12345678,\n  \"path\": \"/project/plans/feature-list/v20260312-143052.json\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Specification\n\n### Plan Ingestion Service API\n\n```typescript\n// Main service export\nexport function createPlanIngestionService(config: PlanStorageConfig): PlanIngestionService;\n\ninterface PlanIngestionService {\n  // Validation\n  validate(content: string): ValidationResult;\n  \n  // Version management\n  save(type: PlanType, content: string, meta: UploadMeta): Promise<SaveResult>;\n  listVersions(type: PlanType): Promise<VersionInfo[]>;\n  getVersion(type: PlanType, version: string): Promise<string | null>;\n  setCurrent(type: PlanType, version: string): Promise<boolean>;\n  getCurrent(type: PlanType): Promise<ActiveMeta | null>;\n  rollback(type: PlanType): Promise<RollbackResult | null>;\n  \n  // Registry\n  getActivePath(type: PlanType): string;\n}\n```\n\n### Command Handler Integration\n\n```typescript\n// In src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js\nexport const planMeta: CommandMeta = {\n  name: 'plan',\n  aliases: ['p'],\n  subcommands: ['status', 'versions', 'use', 'rollback', 'validate'],\n  requiresAuth: true,\n  helpText: '计划文件管理'\n};\n\nexport async function handlePlan(ctx: Context, params: PlanParams): Promise<void>;\n```\n\n---\n\n## Module Dependencies\n\n```\nsrc/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n├── src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js (F-001) - paths\n├── dev-pipeline/templates/feature-list-schema.json\n├── dev-pipeline/templates/bug-fix-list-schema.json\n└── npm: ajv (or zod)\n\nsrc/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js\n├── src/bot/commands/parser.js (F-002)\n├── src/bot/commands/registry.js (F-002)\n├── src/bot/commands/validator.js (F-002)\n├── src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n└── src/services/pipeline-control-service.js (F-001)\n\nsrc/bot/telegram.js (modifications)\n├── src/bot/commands/index.js (F-002)\n├── src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n└── telegraf (existing)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Directory Structure\n\n```\nproject-root/\n├── plans/                          # New directory for versioned plans\n│   ├── feature-list/\n│   │   ├── v20260312-143052.json\n│   │   ├── v20260312-160321.json\n│   │   └── _current.json          # Meta for current version\n│   └── bug-fix-list/\n│       ├── v20260312-143100.json\n│       └── _current.json\n├── feature-list.json               # Symlink to active version (optional)\n├── bug-fix-list.json               # Symlink to active version (optional)\n├── dev-pipeline/\n│   └── templates/\n│       ├── feature-list-schema.json\n│       └── bug-fix-list-schema.json\n└── src/\n    ├── services/\n    │   └── plan-ingestion-service.js  # New\n    └── bot/\n        ├── telegram.js                # Modify\n        └── commands/\n            └── handlers/\n                └── plan.js             # New\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Error Types\n\n| Code | Message | Example |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| `INVALID_JSON` | JSON 解析失败 | 语法错误 |\n| `UNKNOWN_SCHEMA` | 无法识别的 schema 类型 | 缺少 `$schema` 字段 |\n| `SCHEMA_VALIDATION_FAILED` | Schema 校验失败 | 字段类型错误 |\n| `VERSION_NOT_FOUND` | 版本不存在 | 指定版本号无效 |\n| `NO_PREVIOUS_VERSION` | 没有可回滚的版本 | 仅有一个版本 |\n| `FILE_TOO_LARGE` | 文件过大 | 超过限制 |\n| `SAVE_FAILED` | 保存失败 | 文件系统错误 |\n\n### Error Response Format\n\n```typescript\ninterface ValidationErrorDetail {\n  path: string;\n  message: string;\n  example?: string;  // Correct format example\n}\n\nfunction formatValidationErrors(errors: ValidationError[]): string;\n// Output:\n// ❌ 校验失败:\n// • features[0].id: 缺少必填字段 (示例: \"F-001\")\n// • features[1].priority: 必须为正整数 (当前值: -1)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Test Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Module | Test Cases |\n|--------|------------|\n| `plan-ingestion-service.js` | Schema 校验成功/失败、版本保存/切换/回滚、错误处理 |\n| `handlers/plan.js` | Mock service，验证命令参数解析与调用 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Scenario | Test |\n|----------|------|\n| 文件上传流程 | 模拟 Telegram document 消息，验证完整保存流程 |\n| 版本切换 | 验证切换后 pipeline 使用正确文件 |\n| 错误隔离 | 验证校验失败不影响当前生效版本 |\n\n### Test Files\n\n```\ntests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\ntests/bot/commands/handlers/plan.test.js\ntests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js\n```\n\n---\n\n## Risk Assessment\n\n| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|--------|------------|\n| Schema 演进不兼容 | Medium | Medium | 版本化 schema，提供迁移指南 |\n| 大文件上传超时 | Low | Medium | 限制文件大小，分块处理 |\n| 版本切换竞态 | Low | High | 使用文件锁或原子操作 |\n| 磁盘空间耗尽 | Low | Medium | 限制最大版本数，定期清理 |\n\n---\n\n## User Story Mapping\n\n| User Story | Components | Tasks |\n|------------|------------|-------|\n| US-1: Upload Plan File | document handler, plan-ingestion-service | T-100, T-101 |\n| US-2: Schema Validation | validator, schema loader | T-010, T-011 |\n| US-3: Version Management | version manager, plan registry | T-012, T-013, T-102, T-103 |\n| US-4: Plan Status Query | status handler, formatter | T-104 |\n| US-5: Plan Integrity | save logic, error handling | T-014, T-105 |\n| US-6: Pipeline Integration | registry, pipeline-control-service | T-015, T-106 |\n\n---\n\n## Integration Points\n\n### With F-001 (Pipeline Infrastructure)\n\n- 复用 `loadPipelineInfraConfig()` 获取路径配置\n- 扩展配置支持 `plansDir` 参数\n- pipeline-control-service 接受动态 `listPath`\n\n### With F-002 (Command Router)\n\n- 复用 `registerCommand()` 注册 `/plan` 命令\n- 复用 `routeCommand()` 处理命令路由\n- 复用 `validator.js` 验证命令参数\n"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":54845,"output_tokens":3632,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_24a