":"T-101: Implement /plan upload command hint","activeForm":"Implementing /plan upload hint","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-102: Implement /plan versions command","activeForm":"Implementing /plan versions command","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-103: Implement /plan use command","activeForm":"Implementing /plan use command","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-104: Implement /plan status command","activeForm":"Implementing /plan status command","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-105: Implement /plan rollback command","activeForm":"Implementing /plan rollback command","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-106: Implement /plan validate command","activeForm":"Implementing /plan validate command","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-901: Unit tests for plan-ingestion-service","activeForm":"Writing unit tests for plan-ingestion-service","status":"completed"},{"content":"T-902: Integration tests for F-003","activeForm":"Writing integration tests for F-003","status":"completed"}]},"renderer":{"type":"todo"}}}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_755432d442994e7e934f6334","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:27:40.012Z","_requestId":"553c6d77d2214d40857e104dd24ea2b3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"2cd2d2ac-e0a3-4990-901a-1bd8c890924c","session_id":"45f4067c-7723-49aa-b1cf-9e2f92230067","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_755432d442994e7e934f6334","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ F-003 Implementation Complete\n\nAll 18 tasks for feature F-003 (Feature and Bug Plan Ingestion) have been implemented successfully. Here's a summary:\n\n### Setup Phase (T-001, T-002, T-003) ✅\n- Created `plans/feature-list/` and `plans/bug-fix-list/` directories\n- Updated `.gitignore` to ignore version files but keep `_current.json`\n- Installed `ajv@8.18.0` for JSON Schema validation\n- Extended `config-loader.js` with `plansDir` configuration\n\n### Foundational Phase (T-010 through T-015) ✅\n- **T-010**: Schema loader using Ajv for `feature-list-schema.json` and `bug-fix-list-schema.json`\n- **T-011**: Plan validator with schema type detection and field-level errors\n- **T-012**: Version manager with timestamp-based naming (`vYYYYMMDD-HHMMSS`)\n- **T-013**: Plan registry with `_current.json` for current version tracking\n- **T-014**: Error formatting with Chinese messages and field paths\n- **T-015**: Pipeline integration with `resolvePlanListPath()` function\n\n### User Stories Phase (T-100 through T-106) ✅\n- **T-100**: Document upload handler in `telegram.js` for JSON file processing\n- **T-101**: `/plan` command hint showing usage instructions\n- **T-102**: `/plan versions <type>` - list historical versions\n- **T-103**: `/plan use <type> <version>` - switch to specific version\n- **T-104**: `/plan status [type]` - show current plan status\n- **T-105**: `/plan rollback <type>` - rollback to previous version (US-3)\n- **T-106**: `/plan validate` - validation guidance\n\n### Polish Phase (T-901, T-902) ✅\n- Unit tests in `tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js`\n- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js`\n\n### Key Files Created/Modified:\n- `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js` (new)\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js` (new)\n- `src/bot/telegram.js` (modified - added document handler)\n- `src/services/pipeline-control-service.js` (modified - added resolvePlanListPath)\n- `src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js` (modified - added plansDir)\n- `tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js` (new)\n- `tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js` (new)\n- `plans/` directory structure (new)\n- `.gitignore` (modified)\n- `package.json` (modified - added ajv dependency)\n\n[Agent ID: agent-20a0fe99]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_755432d442994e7e934f6334","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:27:53.923Z","_requestId":"553c6d77d2214d40857e104dd24ea2b3"}
